# 6. Solution 3: Monotonic Stack ⭐⭐⭐⭐

## Core Idea 核心

```
找“凹槽” (find basins)
```

Maintain:

```
递减栈 (decreasing stack)
```

---

## Why store index

必须存 index：

1. 需要算宽度
2. 可能有重复值
3. 需要定位位置

---

## Key Logic 关键逻辑

当：

```
height[i] > height[stack[-1]]
```

说明：

```
找到右边界
```

---

## Water Calculation

```
width = right - left - 1
height = min(left_height, right_height) - bottom_height
```

---

## Code

```python
def trap(height):
    stack = []
    res = 0

    for i in range(len(height)):

        while stack and height[i] > height[stack[-1]]:

            bottom = stack.pop()

            if not stack:
                break

            left = stack[-1]

            width = i - left - 1
            h = min(height[left], height[i]) - height[bottom]

            res += width * h

        stack.append(i)

    return res
```

---

## Step-by-step 流程

1. 维护递减栈
2. 遇到更高元素开始弹栈
3. 弹出的作为底部
4. 栈顶作为左边界
5. 当前 i 是右边界
6. 计算水量
7. 累加

---

## Complexity

Time: O(n)  
Space: O(n)

---

# 7. Comparison

| Method | Time | Space | Notes |
|------|------|------|------|
| DP | O(n) | O(n) | easiest |
| Two Pointers | O(n) | O(1) | best |
| Stack | O(n) | O(n) | hardest |

